.TH DOTFILES 7 "2026-03-12" "dotfiles" "Dotfiles Reference"
.SH NAME
dotfiles \- personal system configuration reference
.SH DESCRIPTION
Quick reference for which config file controls what in this dotfiles setup.
All config files live in
.B ~/.dotfiles/
and are symlinked to their expected locations.
.P
Cross-platform: macOS (Homebrew) and Arch Linux (pacman).
.
.SH CONFIGURATION FILES
All paths are relative to
.BR ~/.dotfiles/ .
.P
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Setting|Config File
=
Terminal|ghostty/config
Editor|nvim/
Shell|zsh/zshrc
Login Shell (PATH)|zsh/zprofile
Local Overrides|~/.zshrc.local
Multiplexer|tmux/tmux.conf
Git|git/gitconfig
Git Email (per-machine)|~/.gitconfig.local
Man Page|man/dotfiles.7
Window Manager (Linux)|hyprland/hyprland.conf
Status Bar (Linux)|waybar/config.jsonc + style.css
App Launcher (Linux)|rofi/config.rasi
Power Menu (Linux)|rofi/powermenu.sh
Notifications (Linux)|dunst/dunstrc
Wallpaper (Linux)|~/.config/hypr/hyprpaper.conf
Lock Screen (Linux)|~/.config/hypr/hyprlock.conf
Window Manager (macOS)|aerospace/aerospace.toml
.TE
.
.SH SYMLINKS
Created by
.B install.sh
\(em maps repo files to where the system expects them.
.P
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb | cb
l | l | l .
Repository Source|Symlink Target|Platform
=
nvim/|~/.config/nvim|All
tmux/tmux.conf|~/.tmux.conf|All
zsh/zshrc|~/.zshrc|All
zsh/zprofile|~/.zprofile|All
git/gitconfig|~/.gitconfig|All
git/gitignore_global|~/.gitignore_global|All
ghostty/|~/.config/ghostty|All
aerospace/|~/.config/aerospace|macOS
hyprland/|~/.config/hypr|Linux
waybar/|~/.config/waybar|Linux
rofi/|~/.config/rofi|Linux
dunst/|~/.config/dunst|Linux
man/dotfiles.7|~/.local/share/man/man7/dotfiles.7|Linux
.TE
.
