.SH KEYBINDINGS
.SS Neovim (Leader: Space)
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Keys|Action
=
kj|Exit insert/visual/terminal mode
gcc / gc|Comment line / selection (native)
Space + e|File explorer (netrw)
Space + dd|File explorer in current file dir
Space + ff|Find files (Telescope)
Space + fr|Recent files (Telescope)
Space + fg|Live grep (Telescope)
Space + fb|List buffers (Telescope)
Space + sv / sh|Split vertical / horizontal
Ctrl + h/j/k/l|Navigate splits
Space + +/-|Increment / decrement number
Space + Space|Clear search highlights
Space + tt|Terminal split
Space + cs|Toggle symbol sidebar (aerial)
Space + xx|Toggle diagnostics panel (trouble)
Space + lg|LazyGit
.TE
.SS Neovim LSP (active in files with LSP)
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Keys|Action
=
gd|Go to definition
gr|Show references
K|Hover documentation
Space + ca|Code action (quick fixes)
Space + rn|Rename symbol
Space + d|Line diagnostics
[d / ]d|Previous / next diagnostic
.TE
.SS tmux (Prefix: Ctrl-A)
.TS
box tab(@);
cb | cb
l | l .
Keys@Action
=
Ctrl-A |@Split vertical
Ctrl-A -@Split horizontal
Ctrl-A h/j/k/l@Navigate panes
Ctrl-A H/J/K/L@Resize panes
Ctrl-A c@New window
Ctrl-A [, v, y@Copy mode (vim-style)
Ctrl-A r@Reload config
.TE
.SS Hyprland (Mod: SUPER / Windows key) \(em Linux only
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Keys|Action
=
SUPER + Enter|Terminal (Ghostty)
SUPER + d|App launcher (Rofi)
SUPER + q|Close window
SUPER + h/j/k/l|Move focus
SUPER + Shift + h/j/k/l|Move window
SUPER + Ctrl + h/j/k/l|Resize window
SUPER + f|Fullscreen
SUPER + v|Toggle floating
SUPER + 1-9|Switch workspace
SUPER + Shift + 1-9|Move to workspace
Print|Screenshot (region)
Shift + Print|Screenshot (full)
SUPER + `|Lock screen (hyprlock)
SUPER + Delete|Power menu (lock/logout/reboot/shutdown)
SUPER + Shift + e|Quit Hyprland
.TE
.SS AeroSpace (Mod: Alt) \(em macOS only
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Keys|Action
=
Alt + h/j/k/l|Focus window
Alt + Shift + h/j/k/l|Move/swap window
Alt + Shift + m|Fullscreen
Alt + Shift + e|Balance sizes
Alt + Shift + t|Toggle float/tiling
Ctrl + 1-8|Switch workspace
Ctrl + Shift + 1-8|Move window to workspace
Alt + Tab|Workspace back-and-forth
Alt + Shift + ;|Enter service mode
.TE
.
.SH EDITING CONFIGURATIONS
To edit a config, open the file in Neovim and reload:
.P
.RS 4
.nf
nvim ~/.dotfiles/hyprland/hyprland.conf
hyprctl reload
.fi
.RE
.P
Waybar requires a restart:
.P
.RS 4
.nf
killall waybar && waybar &
.fi
.RE
.
